{"tid":568900,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"大家係點樣放㡳Ex?","createTime":"2018-02-22T08:24:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-14T12:34:42.000Z","uid":7686,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"647e4474e10a34186b420f52c1dafe42e15e9099","tid":568900,"uid":7686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T08:24:25.000Z","msg":"雖然雖然已經過咗三個幾月，但我每一日都好掛住佢。<br />\n我好想去補償我之前做得唔好嘅地方，我實在欠佢太多。<br />\n之前試過幾次箍煲 但係佢已經好決絕咁同我講：「無野要講，唔會再有機會，我已經好討厭你，唔好再騷擾我。你之後點樣都唔關我事」<br />\n<br />\n我知道我唔會有再機會，但係我真係好掛住佢。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n有冇人可以教我點樣去放低Ex <br />\n<br />\nPS 試過約一個女仔出嚟玩 完左之後反而令我更加覺得我係好鍾意Ex...."},{"pid":"2c81ea27c750a418672eb378577de91fead573f8","tid":568900,"uid":78622,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T08:25:18.000Z","msg":"邊條底？"},{"pid":"f9d374f9a06c78526e61d1917a02e1b3a488c181","tid":568900,"uid":138138,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T08:26:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/22/162603_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F22%2F162603_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=38d6b294&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2340efb352344ef8290dadf8c925741f4e3f88f4","tid":568900,"uid":143471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T08:27:55.000Z","msg":"識第個"},{"pid":"b5d44343e2e5e679c0220758e56564b670317916","tid":568900,"uid":7686,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"2340efb352344ef8290dadf8c925741f4e3f88f4","tid":568900,"uid":143471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T08:27:55.000Z","msg":"識第個"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T08:29:26.000Z","msg":"試過 早兩日咋嘛 但係我真係唔想騎牛搵馬"},{"pid":"71c05